{"tid":1376582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 警方：正在西區作出驅散行動","createTime":"2019-07-28T11:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:24:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f554800702e7a3ddc85e858e5686de86eaa5fd45","tid":1376582,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"警方現正在西區作出驅散行動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n  今日（七月二十八日）晚上約七時，一批示威者集結在西區警署附近一帶馬路，向警察防線投擲磚頭。鑑於現場情況正在急劇惡化，警方現正由西向東進行驅散行動，並施放催淚煙。警方呼籲，在場人士盡快離開，切勿衝擊警方防線。市民如非必要，切勿前往有關地區。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月28日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間19時04分"},{"pid":"153497409916095f5ca45aeee8f526f091e2d6a6","tid":1376582,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800747.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F28%2FP2019072800747.htm&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f090ddc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800747.htm</a>"},{"pid":"75f96bdfc9525e64f31e10b2bce1aa98a1351970","tid":1376582,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed7dca05f4e3e47d29149393a8bab04a63c5c3f","tid":1376582,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b17e24657d557bf88755e56e93c9082067f579c","tid":1376582,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n三毛五毛見分化